-- Debt-Ridden Euro Nations Must Reform to End Crisis, Estonia Says
-- B y   O t t   U m m e l a s
-- 2012-10-24T08:00:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-24/debt-ridden-euro-nations-must-reform-to-end-crisis-estonia-says.html
Estonia’s central bank said the euro
region’s debt-ridden economies must carry out structural changes
and adhere to European Union budget rules to put an end to the
sovereign-debt crisis, according to a policy document released
today in the capital, Tallinn.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ott Ummelas in Tallinn at 
 oummelas@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
